<div class="seriesContainer mar30t">
<p class="text-center"><img src="/files/summerBanner4.jpg" alt="logo" width="636" height="200" /></p>
<p>Looking for a way to turn up your summer fun on behalf of a great cause? Why not bring your friends, family and community together with a summer themed fundraiser in support of Team Fox! From lemonade stands and backyard BBQs to pool parties and kickball tournaments, the possibilities are endless! While you can transform almost any interest or passion into a fundraiser, check out a few ideas below to get started.</p>
<p>As a Summer Series fundraiser, you’ll be equipped with a wealth of tools and resources, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>An online fundraising page with a unique URL that can be customized with a personal story, event information and photo or video.</li>
<li>An online Participant Center to serve as your fundraising headquarters through which you can email friends and family members, track donations, share your story, and more.</li>
<li>The Team Fox Handbook, a 20+ page guide to help you maximize your fundraising and event planning.</li>
<li>Access to the Team Fox logo, banners, and other collateral items to give your event additional legitimacy.</li>
<li>Assistance from the Team Fox staff and/or a Team Fox mentor.</li>
<li>A Team Fox t-shirt to sport!</li>
</ul>
<h2 style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;">Scroll over the images below to learn more!</h2>
